#: 3cddbe46ba3c481da7160eee66fa4934
msgid ""
"Before the Bass model, companies struggled to predict the adoption "
"patterns of new products. Traditional forecasting methods often failed "
"because they couldn't account for the social dynamics that drive product "
"adoption. Frank Bass recognized that product adoption follows a distinct "
"pattern:"
msgstr ""

